snippet.title: Confidence, Masculinity, Faith and Fatherhood
snippet.description:
0:00 Intro
6:31 Confidence and Masculinity
17:00 "I never understood what dating meant" and 'situationships'
30:00 Masculine Hobbies
42:05 Looking for 'signs' from God, signs that can lead you astray
1:02:00 The "Ride or Die" chick
1:14:00 "Love God because only He will love you."
1:16:30 How has fatherhood changed you?
1:23:00 Mary, Sorrowful Mysteries
1:29:24 "If I didn't have faith in God, I don't know if I would still be alive."
